HEADWORD: Napoleonic
<hw>Na*po`le*on"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Of or
pertaining to <persfn>Napoleon I.</persfn>, or his family; resembling,
or having the qualities of, <person>Napoleon I.</person></def>
